      <title id="i2127121" xtrc="GSAR" xtrf="GSAR" class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">512.301</ph> Solicitation provisions and
contract clauses for the acquisition of commercial items.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d213e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li id="TKNNCz" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d211e17" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Contract
clauses</i>
                  <ph id="s86x9de" class="- topic/ph ">.
Insert the following clauses in solicitations and contracts for
the acquisition of commercial items:</ph>
               </p>
               <ol id="d213e26" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li id="oLryJZ" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d211e30" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        <ph id="pfrjhfn" class="- topic/ph ">The clause at <xref href="GSAM-i1876001.dita#i1876001"
                                 outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                 class="- topic/xref ">552.212-71</xref>,
Contract Terms and Conditions Applicable to GSA Acquisition of Commercial
Items. This clause incorporates by reference only those clauses
required to implement GSA requirements applicable to the acquisition
of commercial items. This clause may be tailored in accordance with
FAR <xref href="https://www.acquisition.gov/far/part-12#FAR_12_302"
                                 format="html"
                                 scope="external"
                                 class="- topic/xref ">12.302</xref> and GSAM <xref href="GSAM-AAWGVUMU.dita#AAWGVUMU"
                                 outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                 class="- topic/xref ">512.302</xref>.</ph>
                     </p>
                  </li>
                  <li id="HYattF" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d211e42" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        <ph id="hvs91itj" class="- topic/ph ">The clause at <xref href="GSAM-i1876237.dita#i1876237"
                                 outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                 class="- topic/xref ">552.212-72</xref>,
Contract Terms and Conditions Required to Implement Statutes or
Executive Orders Applicable to GSA Acquisitions of Commercial Items,
when any listed clauses therein apply. This clause incorporates by
reference only those clauses required to implement provisions of
law or Executive orders that apply to commercial item acquisitions.</ph>
                     </p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li id="BrCikP" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d211e56" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  <ph id="plgn8h3h" class="- topic/ph ">
                     <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">FAR deviation</i>. GSA
has a FAR deviation that allows use of the clause at <xref href="GSAM-YMIBGEPW.dita#YMIBGEPW"
                           outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                           class="- topic/xref ">552.212-4</xref> in
lieu of the FAR clause at <xref href="https://www.acquisition.gov/far/part-52#FAR_52_212_4"
                           format="html"
                           scope="external"
                           class="- topic/xref ">52.212-4</xref>. Insert the
clause at <xref href="GSAM-YMIBGEPW.dita#YMIBGEPW"
                           outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                           class="- topic/xref ">552.212-4</xref>, Contract Terms
and Conditions-Commercial Items, in lieu of the FAR clause at <xref href="https://www.acquisition.gov/far/part-52#FAR_52_212_4"
                           format="html"
                           scope="external"
                           class="- topic/xref ">52.212-4</xref>. Use the
clause with its Alternate I in lieu of the FAR clause at <xref href="https://www.acquisition.gov/far/part-52#FAR_52_212_4"
                           format="html"
                           scope="external"
                           class="- topic/xref ">52.212-4</xref> and its Alternate
I. This clause may be tailored in accordance with FAR <xref href="https://www.acquisition.gov/far/part-12#FAR_12_302"
                           format="html"
                           scope="external"
                           class="- topic/xref ">12.302</xref> and GSAM <xref href="GSAM-AAWGVUMU.dita#AAWGVUMU"
                           outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                           class="- topic/xref ">512.302</xref>.</ph>
               </p>
            </li>
            <li id="oitzkC" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d211e68" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  <ph id="ald21z1p" class="- topic/ph ">
                     <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Discretionary use of
GSAR provisions and clauses</i>. Consistent with the limitations
contained in FAR <xref href="https://www.acquisition.gov/far/part-12#FAR_12_302"
                           format="html"
                           scope="external"
                           class="- topic/xref ">12.302</xref> and <xref href="GSAM-AAWGVUMU.dita#AAWGVUMU"
                           outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                           class="- topic/xref ">512.302</xref>,
the contracting officer may include in solicitations and contracts
by addendum other GSAR provisions and clauses.</ph>
               </p>
            </li>
            <li id="IyvLJA" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d211e101" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Use of additional provisions
and clauses</i>
                  <ph id="t3wy0gag" class="- topic/ph ">.
The Senior Procurement Executive shall approve the use of a provision
or clause that is either not:</ph>
               </p>
               <ol id="d213e107" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li id="YznSfh" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d211e111" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        <ph id="wq5l5y4" class="- topic/ph ">Prescribed in the FAR or
GSAR for use in acquisitions for commercial items.</ph>
                     </p>
                  </li>
                  <li id="xDhRWw" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d211e120" audience="GSAR" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        <ph id="2lcs0k7" class="- topic/ph ">Consistent with customary
commercial practice.</ph>
                     </p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
